<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Sub-Admin Account Created</title>
</head>

<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f3f4f6; margin: 0; padding: 20px;">
    <div
        style="max-width: 600px; margin: 30px auto; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; color: #333;">
        <h2 style="color: #1a202c;">👋 Welcome, <%= fname %>!</h2>
        <p>Your sub-admin account has been successfully created. Below are your login credentials and access details:
        </p>

        <h3 style="color: #2563eb;">🔐 Login Credentials</h3>
        <p>
            <strong>Email:</strong>
            <%= email %><br />
                <strong>Password:</strong>
                <%= password %>
        </p>

        <p style="margin-top: 20px;">🔁 We recommend changing your password after your first login.</p>

        <div
            style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 0.85em; color: #888888; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; padding-top: 10px;">
            <p>© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Your Company. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>